      • build

        public SyncDelta build()
        Creates a SyncDelta. Prior to calling the following must be specified:
        1. Object (for anything other than delete)
        2. Uid (this is implictly set when calling setObject(ConnectorObject))
        3. Token
        4. DeltaType
